17.title: Sumit's Interview with Kapil Dev
17.plot: Maya, Aliya and Avi fall sick. Sumit has an interview with Kapil Dev. He takes Aliya to the doctor. Kapil refuses to be interviewed at the clinic. Dolly takes care of Maya in Sumit's absence. Sumit gets Aliya's checkup done. He reschedules his interview with Kapil. Later, Kapil falls sick as well.

18.title: Sumit's Funeral Speech
18.plot: Jasbir asks Sumit to prepare a speech for his grandfather's funeral. Dolly's sister, Minti, comes visiting. Maya helps Sumit with his speech. Dolly is upset with Sumit for supporting Minti. Sumit forgets his speech. Later, he tries to make things right between Dolly and Minti.

19.title: Sumit and the fake diamond ring
19.plot: Rajneesh arrests Jasbir's friend, Bittu, for selling fake diamonds. Sumit worries as he had bought Maya's ring from Bittu. He steals the ring from Maya, but later, learns that she had replaced the diamond with an original one. Maya makes Sumit find the diamond on learning that he has thrown it away.

21.title: Jasbir's Birthday Celebration
21.plot: The Walias celebrate Jasbir's birthday. Dolly gifts him a sweater. Sumit tells Rajneesh that he has ordered a fish tank for Jasbir. Sumit comforts a depressed Jasbir when a fish dies in the tank.

22.title: The Health-conscious Walias
22.plot: Dolly tells Sumit about her and Jasbir's medical reports. Maya tells Sumit that Dolly wants to learn how to cook healthy food. Later, Dolly insists that Jasbir, Rajneesh and Sumit eat right. She is upset when Sumit orders food from a restaurant and Sumit is shocked when he sees Dolly eating chicken.

23.title: Sumit at Harsha Bhogle's show
23.plot: Sumit is elated as Avi says 'Papa' as his first word. He is nervous during his interview with Harsha Bhogle. Later, Maya, Jasbir and Dolly point out Sumit's mistake in the interview. Sumit messes up his interview with Harsha, once again. Later, he asks for Dolly, Jasbir, Maya and Rajnish's feedback.

24.title: Dolly confronts Maya
24.plot: Maya confronts Sumit as Rajneesh misbehaves with Simran in the market. She tells Rajneesh that she will introduce Simran to Dolly. Later, Sumit introduces Simran to Dolly. Sumit tells Dolly that Rajneesh and Simran are friends. Dolly is upset with Maya for lying to her about Simran.

25.title: Jasbir-Dolly: Wedding Anniversary
25.plot: Maya, Sumit and Rajneesh plan a surprise wedding anniversary party for Jasbir-Dolly. Sumit gets annoyed when Jasbir-Dolly pick a fight with each other. He tells Maya, that their future will be the same as Jasbir-Dolly's present.

26.title: Maya's Got a New Maid
26.plot: Maya introduces Sumit to their new maid, Chanda. Later, Dolly assures Maya of taking care of her children. Maya decides to fire Chanda. She apologises to Dolly for her mistake. Dolly is injured while playing with Aliya and Avi. Sumit asks Chanda to rejoin.

27.title: Maya's Parents Versus Sumit's
27.plot: Sumit invites Jasbir and Dolly to meet Maya's parents. Maya's mother decides to go to a Japanese restaurant. Sumit feels embarrassed when Dolly and Jasbir order Indian food. Later, he sides with his parents and insults Maya's parents. Maya throws Sumit out of the house for his behaviour.

29.title: Sumit takes care of ghar kharcha
29.plot: Maya asks Sumit to manage the household expenses. Sumit is shocked to learn that he has paid Rs 2.5 lakh instead of Rs 25,000 by mistake. He takes money from Rajneesh, but fails to deposit it in his account. Maya tries to make Sumit realise his mistake.

30.title: Jasbir Wins an Award
30.plot:

31.title: Walias Simran le jaayenge
31.plot: Dolly is surprised to see Simran. Rajneesh tells Sumit that Simran will prepare dinner for the family. Sumit tells Maya that Dolly likes Simran the most and lies to Dolly that Maya sings bhajans. Dolly confronts Sumit for lying to her. Jasbir reveals Dolly's boyfriend to the family.

32.title: Maya refuses to do Avi's mundan
32.plot: Maya talks about Avi's first day at the play school to Sumit. Jasbir and Dolly decide to get Avi tonsured, but Maya refuses. Jasbir tells Sumit that Kallu will shave Avi's hair. Will Sumit agree?

33.title: Sumit's Reunion Party
33.plot: Jasbir and Dolly show Sumit's childhood photographs to Maya. Maya learns about Sumit's reunion party. Sumit introduces Maya to his friend, Shaunti. Sumit's friends make fun of him at the reunion party. Sumit confronts Maya for dancing with his friend at the reunion party.

34.title: Rajneesh Arrests the Goons
34.plot: Rajneesh asks Sumit to accompany him for patrolling. Maya allows Sumit to go with Rajneesh for patrolling. Rajneesh confronts Sumit for making fun of him. He arrests a few goons for teasing a girl. Rajneesh confronts Sumit for taking credit of arresting the goons.

35.title: Jasbir Tries Bungee Jumping
35.plot: Sumit is excited about his work trip to London, but is upset when the trip is cancelled. Maya is annoyed with Sumit's boring wish list. Sumit is depressed as he feels that he has no goal in life. Jasbir and Dolly tell Sumit about their dreams and Jasbir tries bungee jumping.

36.title: Jasbir, the Rash Driver
36.plot: Rajneesh tells Sumit that Jasbir has hit a police jeep. Maya decides not to send her children with Jasbir as he is a rash driver. Sumit asks Jasbir to get his driving license and tells Maya that Jasbir has passed the driving test.

37.title: Pests Inside Dolly's House
37.plot: Maya and Sumit tell Dolly about the pest control at their house. Dolly asks them to stay at her house. Maya plans to annoy Dolly. Sumit shares a room with Rajneesh. Watch Maya and Sumit turning Dolly's house upside down.

38.title: Maya Writes a Letter to Dolly
38.plot: Sumit invites his friends to watch a cricket match, while Maya throws a kitty party. Dolly decides to prepare desi pasta for the party. Maya is upset about Dolly's interference in her life and sends her a letter. Later, Maya regrets sending the letter to Dolly and apologises to her.

39.title: Rajneesh Leaves the House
39.plot: Rajneesh shares a private moment with Simran, when his family interrupts him. Sumit provokes Rajneesh to leave the house. Maya asks Sumit to bring Rajneesh back as Dolly has decided to spend time with them. Sumit meets Rajneesh and makes him realise that his landlords are similar to Jasbir and Dolly.

40.title: Sumit lies to Maya
40.plot: Maya asks Sumit to take Avi and Aliya to a kids-zone. Maya's friends praise Sumit for supporting them. Later, Rajneesh and Jasbir are shocked to notice Sumit and Maya's strange behaviour, towards each other. Jasbir tries to make Maya realise her mistake. Maya confronts Sumit for lying to her.

41.title: Sumit apologises to Maya
41.plot: Sumit apologises to Maya on Jasbir's behalf. Maya suffers from a cold. She gets irritated as Jasbir, Dolly and Rajneesh disturb her. Sumit reminds Maya about her wish to live with his parents, a few years ago. Maya regrets her mistake. The Walias celebrate Avi's birthday.

42.title: Rajneesh-Simran Break Up
42.plot: Sumit stays at home to receive the delivery of the new curtains, while Rajneesh enjoys freedom in his new apartment. Sumit tells Rajneesh about the downside of marriage. Maya scolds Sumit as Rajneesh and Simran break up because of him. Sumit tries to convince Rajneesh to get back with Simran.

43.title: The Sumit-Maya Fight!
43.plot: Dolly asks Sumit what's bothering him. He tells her about his argument with Maya. Meanwhile, Maya shares her sorrows with Rajneesh. Later, Maya and Sumit apologise to each other for their mistakes. Maya is upset with Sumit for complaining to Jasbir and Dolly about her.

44.title: Maya's Teacher Visits the Walias
44.plot: Maya tells Sumit that her school teacher, Mrs Mathur will be visiting them. She introduces her to Sumit. Later, Sumit introduces Jasbir and Dolly to Mrs Mathur. Maya is jealous when Mrs Mathur praises the Walias. Seeing this, Sumit too praises Maya.

45.title: Sumit proves his manhood
45.plot: Maya calls Sumit effeminate as he fails to help her while she chokes on an orange seed. Later, Sumit arm wrestles with Jasbir to prove his manliness. Sumit ends up injuring Maya while he tries to remove a splinter lodged in her finger. Rajneesh and his friends mock Sumit.

46.title: Rajneesh introduces Preeti
46.plot: Dolly and Maya ask Sumit to meet Rajneesh, who introduces his neighbour, Preeti to him. Sumit informs Maya that Rajneesh is depressed after his breakup with Simran. Later, Sumit is shocked to see Dolly and Jasbir at Rajneesh's house. Preeti invites Rajneesh to a party.

47.title: Maya Attends the Interview
47.plot: Maya informs Sumit that she wants to start working. She informs Dolly that she will attend an interview. Maya tells Sumit that she has secured a job. Later, a dejected Maya informs Sumit that she has lost her job. Sumit tries to calm Maya. He asks Maya to search a new job.

48.title: Where There Is a Will
48.plot: Sumit decides to legally draft his will and Maya supports him. They decide to nominate Maya's parents as Avi and Aliya's guardians. However, when they refuse, Sumit is compelled to make Dolly and Jasbir his children's guardians.

49.title: Sumit, Dolly showcase talent
49.plot: Dolly arranges the celebration of the wedding anniversary of her friends, Sheela and Nippy, at her home. Sumit and Maya decide to entertain the guests by imitating Dolly and Jasbir. However, they get offended when Dolly and Jasbir imitate them back.

50.title: The Brothers Make a Plan
50.plot: Rajat, Monty and Puggy refuse to party with Sumit. Sumit tells Rajneesh that Maya has gone to Mumbai. He asks Rajneesh to apologise to Simran. Later, Rajneesh confronts Sumit for trying to frighten him. He apologises to Sumit for his mistake. Sumit and Rajneesh plan to frighten Jasbir.

51.title: Fun Fair at Alia's School
51.plot: Alia tells Maya and Sumit that her class has to run a food stall at a fun fair event. The Walias accompany Alia to the event. The food stall incharge, Purkayastha asks Maya to bring the snacks, but she refuses; Sumit, however, gives them. Jasbir and Rajneesh make fun of him.

52.title: Maya, Rajneesh Go Dancing
52.plot: Maya-Rajneesh go to the disco together on Sumit's advice. Sumit is jealous to learn that Maya enjoys dancing with Rajneesh. He tries to create misunderstandings between the two so that their next outing is cancelled. However, they find out about Sumit's plan and confront him.

53.title: Maya ka IQ Sumit se zyaada?
53.plot: Sumit and Maya give an IQ test to help Rajneesh's promotion. Maya comforts Sumit as he is upset on scoring less than her. Sumit takes advantage of Maya's sympathy and pretends to be upset. Later, Rajneesh tells them that their scores got swapped. Maya and Sumit learn that the test was a hoax.

54.title: Sumit Cheats On Maya
54.plot: Dolly asks Sumit and Jasbir to fast on the occasion of Karva Chauth. Rajneesh tries to stop Jasbir from eating. However, he finds Sumit eating at a restaurant. Maya finds out about Sumit's deed and Jasbir learns about Dolly ending her fast.

55.title: The Walias Argue Over Food
55.plot: Jasbir and Rajneesh praise the Amritsari koftas prepared by Maya. Bobby praises the food and tells Maya about Sumit making fun of her culinary skills. Maya confronts Sumit, while Dolly confronts Maya. Jasbir scolds Sumit for making fun of Maya.

56.title: Sumit Learns about Maya's Debt
56.plot: Sumit informs Maya about Bobby and Puggy's plan to launch their own company. Maya asks Sumit not to invest in their business but he tells her about already giving them Rs 2 lakh. Maya tries to make Sumit realise his folly. However, he learns that Maya herself has borrowed money from Dolly.

57.title: Simran-Rajneesh Reunite
57.plot: Rajneesh and Simran reunite. He is compelled to move into Sumit's house, as his apartment secretary misunderstands his relationship with Simran. The drama unfolds when Dolly learns about Simran-Ranjeesh staying at Sumit's house.

58.title: The Walias Play Table Tennis
58.plot: Dolly restores an old table tennis board for Aliya and Avi to play. Rajneesh teases Sumit for crying during a match with Jasbir. This annoys Sumit and he argues with Jasbir over the victory of a match in his childhood. The drama unfolds when the two challenge each other to a fresh game.

59.title: Snoring Maya Drives Sumit Away
59.plot: Maya's snoring drives Sumit to sleep in the living room. Later, Maya stays up all night to allow Sumit a peaceful sleep. Jasbir tells Sumit about curing Dolly's snoring problem, by showering her with love. However, Sumit fails to put Jasbir's idea into practice.

60.title: Ek Family Photo Ho Jaaye
60.plot: Sumit buys a photo frame to gift Maya's mother on her birthday. Dolly asks Sumit for a photo frame as well. She intends to have a family picture taken and becomes upset when Maya's parents and Simran show up for the photoshoot. Sumit loses his temper trying to manage both the families.

61.title: Dolly and Maya in a Pickle!
61.plot: Dolly asks Maya to return her pickle jar, which is of some sentimental value. Maya claims to have returned it. An argument ensures between them and Dolly apologises for her misgivings. Later, Maya realises that the pickle jar is actually in her house and struggles to smuggle it back to Dolly's house.

62.title: Dolly Ruins Rajneesh's Chance
62.plot: Rajneesh tells Maya about the CBI interview scheduled for him. Later, Rajneesh informs Sumit that Dolly had sent a fax to Khurana, the Deputy Director of the CBI. He blames Dolly for ruining his interview and asks her to stay away from him. Dolly apologises to Khurana for her mistake.

63.title: Maya-Dolly Argue Over Laddoos
63.plot: Maya advises Sumit to host a Diwali dinner at their house. She asks Sumit to tell Dolly that she would prepare the food. Later, Sumit tells Maya that Dolly has invited their relatives. Maya argues with Dolly over the preparation of laddoos.

64.title: Maya Ignores Dolly's Taunts
64.plot: Maya tells Sumit that she has invited Simran for dinner. Later, Maya decides not react to Dolly's taunts. She tells Sumit that her lack of response has made Dolly stop her taunts. Jasbir makes fun of Sumit. Dolly tries to make Maya realise her mistake. Jasbir and Rajneesh apologise to Sumit.

65.title: Maya Contests Election
65.plot: Maya informs Sumit about elections for the chairman of the parent-teacher association. She tells him about the candidate announcement. Maya informs Rajneesh that she has lost the election. Maya yells at Sumit for not voting for her.

66.title: Rajneesh Is Hospitalised
66.plot: Sumit lies to Rajneesh about his work. Jasbir informs Sumit about Rajneesh's hospitalisation. Later, Sumit makes fun of Rajneesh as he learns that a bull had attacked him from the rear. He confesses to Rajneesh about attending the party. Later, Sumit apologises to Rajneesh.

67.title: Sumit-Maya Wed Again!
67.plot: Maya feels upset as Sumit records a cricket match over their wedding DVD. Dolly advises Sumit to remarry Maya. Maya feels excited as Sumit shares the idea with her. The guests arrive for the wedding. Maya delivers a wedding speech for Sumit. However, when it's his turn, Sumit becomes speechless.

68.title: Dolly Blackmails Sumit
68.plot: Maya wants Dolly to make new friends. Sumit suggests that Dolly should invite the Ahluwalias home. Later, Dolly and Jasbir bring the Ahluwalias to Sumit's house instead. Maya tells Sumit to go away before the Ahluwalias arrive. Dolly emotionally blackmails Sumit to spend time with them.

69.title: Sumit Spies on Maya
69.plot: Sumit is stunned to see Maya bleaching her face. He apologises to Maya for his response. Maya tells Sumit that she wants to stay alone for a while. Sumit confides in Dolly, and Jasbir makes fun of him. Later, Maya confronts Sumit for spying on her. She tells Sumit that she is not insane.

70.title: It's Rajneesh's Birthday!
70.plot: Jasbir makes fun of Rajneesh. Maya, Jasbir and Sumit discuss getting Rajneesh a birthday gift. Later, Sumit rebukes Rajneesh for insulting him. The family wishes Rajneesh on his birthday. Jasbir scolds Rajneesh for insulting the family. Rajneesh apologises to Dolly for his misbehaviour.

71.title: Sumit Makes Fun of Maya, Again!
71.plot: Maya reminds Sumit about Happy Uncle's birthday. Later, the Walias celebrate his birthday at their house. Sumit makes fun of Maya's cooking and she gets upset with him for insulting her. Later, she apologises to him. Sumit is worried that Maya might want revenge.

108.title: Rajneesh-Simran Get Married!
108.plot: Jasbir feels bored at Rajneesh-Simran's wedding. Nirmal stops Jasbir from getting drunk. Dolly finds Nirdharit tied up in the bathroom and frees him. Nirmal and Pavitra tell the Walias that Rajneesh will not stay with them after the wedding. Rajneesh and Simran complete the wedding rituals.

imdb.title: Sumit Sambhal Lega
plot: Sumit, a reckless young man, runs away from responsibilities. Moreover, without understanding the seriousness of the situation, he ends up making a mockery of it.
